data.title: Submit order to purchasing dept.
data.description: Using the correct supply form, fill out the details and send the order via email to the Purchasing Department.

data.title: Supply order
data.description: Here is the completed supply form, please look at the Docs section of this node to find the link to download.

data.title: Review supply order
data.description: Meeting between the Purchasing Department and the Manufacturing Department to go over the details on the supply order.

data.title: Order supplies?
data.description: The Purchasing Department will make a decision based on the details on the form as to whether it is ready for purchase. If it is they will submit the order to the supplier. If not they will send it back to the Manufacturing Department.

data.title: Submit order to supplier
data.description: Sending the finished supply order to the Supplier.

data.title: Supply order
data.description: Here is the completed supply form that is prepared to be sent to the Supplier. Please look at the Docs section of this node to find the link to download.

data.title: Fulfill order
data.description: The supplier begins to fulfill the order.

data.title: Supplies
data.description: These are the supplies that were ordered in the supply form.

data.title: Deliver supplies
data.description: The delivery service will pick up the supplies from the supplier and deliver them to their destination.

data.title: Delivered supplies
data.description: These are the delivered supplies that have been successfully delivered to their destination.

data.title: Receive supplies
data.description:
- Supply Order
- Delivered supplies
- Verify supplies match the supply order
- Signed Receipt

data.title: Supply Order
data.description: This is the supply order that was previously submitted.

data.title: Delivered supplies
data.description: These are the delivered supplies that we receive from the delivery service.

data.title: Verify supplies match the supply order
data.description: The manufacturing department will check the delivered supplies and verify receipt.

data.title: Signed Receipt
data.description: This is the signed receipt of the delivery.
